---
title: Tex-Mex Pork Quesadillas with Charred Corn Salsa & Sour Cream
description: Juicy spiced pork, charred corn and melted Cheddar cheese, it’s hard to resist these incredibly delicious quesadillas. Plus, it takes just 30 minutes to have this Tex-Mex feast on your dinner table!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5f30c9397ad4d550e331fe04-865a26c1.jpg
